#. Activity title
#: activities/adjacent_numbers/ActivityInfo.qml:14
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid "Find the adjacent numbers"
msgstr "નજીકની સંખ્યાઓ શોધો"

#. Help title
#: activities/adjacent_numbers/ActivityInfo.qml:16
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid "Find the missing adjacent numbers."
msgstr "ખૂટતા નજીકની સંખ્યાઓ શોધો."

