msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid "Learn subtraction"
msgstr "બાદબાકી શીખો"

#. Help title
#: activities/learn_subtractions/ActivityInfo.qml:17
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid "Learn subtraction with small numbers."
msgstr "નાની સંખ્યાઓ સાથે બાદબાકી શીખો."

#. Help goal
#: activities/learn_subtractions/ActivityInfo.qml:20
