"The|house|is|red.\n"
"The|boy|reads|a book.\n"
"My|friend|is|nice.\n"
"What|a|beautiful|sight!\n"
"Steve|jumps|into|the|pool.\n"
"Jessica|wants|a|new|book.\n"
"Mom|made|me|a|sandwich.\n"
"Tigers|live|in|forests.\n"
"Football|is|a|team|game."
msgstr ""
"The|dog|barks.\n"
"The|house|is|red.\n"
"The|boy|reads|a book.\n"
"My|friend|is|nice.\n"
"What|a|beautiful|sight!\n"
"Steve|jumps|into|the|pool.\n"
"Jessica|wants|a|new|book.\n"
"Mom|made|me|a|sandwich.\n"
