#. Help manual
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/ActivityInfo.qml:23
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid ""
"To balance the scales, move some masses to the left or the right side (on "
"higher levels). They can be arranged in any order. Take care of the weight "
"and the unit of the masses, remember that a pound (lb) is 16 ounce (oz)."
msgstr ""
"ત્રાજવાને સંતુલિત કરવા માટે, ડાબી કે જમણી બાજુએ (ઉચ્ચ સ્તરો પર) થોડા દળ (masses) "
"ખસેડો. તેમને કોઈપણ ક્રમમાં ગોઠવી શકાય છે. દળ અને તેના એકમનું ધ્યાન રાખો, યાદ રાખો કે એક "
"પાઉન્ડ (lb) એટલે 16 ઔંસ (oz)."

#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/1/Data.qml:13
msgctxt "Data|"
msgid "Balance up to 5 ounces."
msgstr "5 ઔંસ સુધી સંતુલિત કરો."

#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/1/Data.qml:18
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/2/Data.qml:18
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/3/Data.qml:18
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:18
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/6/Data.qml:18
#, qt-format
msgctxt "Data|"
msgid "%1 oz"
msgstr "%1 ઔંસ"

#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/1/Data.qml:26
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/2/Data.qml:26
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/3/Data.qml:26
msgctxt "Data|"
msgid ""
"The \"oz\" symbol at the end of a number means ounce. One pound equals "
"sixteen ounces. \n"
" Drop weights on the left side to balance the scales."
msgstr ""
"સંખ્યાની અંતે \"oz\" ચિહ્નનો અર્થ ઔંસ થાય છે. એક પાઉન્ડ એટલે સોળ ઔંસ. \n"
" ત્રાજવાને સંતુલિત કરવા માટે ડાબી બાજુએ વજન મૂકો."

#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/1/Data.qml:39
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/2/Data.qml:45
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/2/Data.qml:52
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/3/Data.qml:47
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/3/Data.qml:54
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:69
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:76
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:83
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:90
#: activities/scalesboard_weight_avoirdupois/resource/5/Data.qml:97
